{{Infobox football club | clubname = Kara-Balta| image = [[Image:FC Jayil-Baatyr.gif|100px|Logo]]| fullname = Kara-Balta| nickname = | founded = | ground = [[Kara-Balta]], [[Kyrgyzstan]]| capacity = | chairman = | manager = | league = Top Liga | season = 2018 | position = 7th| }}
'''Kara-Balta''' is a [[Kyrgyzstan]]i football club based in [[Kara-Balta]], Kyrgyzstan that plays in the top division in Kyrgyzstan, the [[Kyrgyzstan League]].
== History == *1992: Founded as ''KVT Khimik Kara-Balta''. *1995: Renamed ''KVT Dinamo Kara-Balta''. *2001: Renamed ''FC Bakay Kara-Balta''. *2003: Renamed ''FC Jayil-Baatyr Kara-Balta''. *2009: Renamed ''FC Khimik Kara-Balta''. *2015: Renamed ''FC Kara-Balta''.
